PAYMENT PRODUCTS, WE HAVE ESTABLISHED BUSINESS RELATIONSHIPS IN THE MOBILE AND GAMING SPACES TO DRIVE ADOPTION OF THE SERVE SOFTWARE PLATFORM. FOR EXAMPLE, AS A RESULT OF OUR PARTNERSHIP WITH THE LIANLIAN GROUP, THE MOBILE TOP-UP COMPANY HAS

LEVERAGED THE SERVE SOFTWARE PLATFORM IN CONNECTION WITH THE PROCESSING OF CERTAIN TOP-UP TRANSACTIONS IN NINE PROVINCES IN CHINA AS OF THE END OF 2013.

